	<h3>What is User Experience?</h3>
		<p>Have you ever been to a website and it takes you about 20 minutes to fine that one thing you needed and feeling dumb because it was actually pretty easy?</p>
		<p>That is what User Experience tries to avoid, it is focues on giving you the BEST user experience in all sites of the internet.</p>

	<h3>What is UX composed of?</h3>

